System:

    melt of 100 wormlike chains of 8 atoms.

Usage - cd to an example subdirectory, then enter:

MC simulation:

    mcSim -e -p param -c commands

Restart and extend previous simulation

    mdcim -e -r restart -c commands.rst

------------------------------------------------------

BUG: The example in the Reptation subdirectory is 
broken, because of a bug in the implementation of the 
CfbReptation MC move for systems with angle potentials. 
